<div class="blog-posts page-41">
  <div id="post-1516353" class="blog-post position-1 first odd-post"><div class="odd-post-inner blog-post-inner"><h1 class="title"><a href="http://softwarelivre.org/helioloureiro/blog/silenciando-os-absurdos-do-crt-value-is-absurd">Silenciando os absurdos do &quot;_CRT value is absurd&quot;</a></h1><span class="publishing-info"><span class="date">8 de Junho de 2008, 0:00</span><span class="author">, por Home</span><span class="comments"> - <a href="/helioloureiro/blog/silenciando-os-absurdos-do-crt-value-is-absurd#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>sem comentários ainda</span></a></span></span><div>
<p><img src="http://helio.loureiro.eng.br/images/stories/virus.gif" border="0">Cansado de ver as mensagens surgindo o tempo todo:</p>
<pre>acpi_tz0: _CRT value is absurd, ignored (256.0C) 
acpi_tz0: _CRT value is absurd, ignored (256.0C) 
acpi_tz0: _CRT value is absurd, ignored (256.0C) 
